    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg prose-gray">

      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing and using the website <strong>dairia-law.com</strong> (the "Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, please do not use the Site.
