      </p>

      <h2>4. DAIRIA AI — Artificial Intelligence Tools</h2>
      <p>
        DAIRIA AI is an AI-powered legal assistant. Important limitations:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>AI responses are <strong>informational only</strong> and do not replace legal counsel</li>
